jcr:content.jcr:title: NEOM partners with KAUST to create the world's largest coral garden
jcr:content.jcr:description: NEOM Company and King Abdullah University of Science and Technology (KAUST) today announced a joint project to establish the world's largest coral garden at Shushah Island in the Red Sea area of NEOM, in northwest Saudi Arabia.
